@startuml
package "QLearningAgent" {

  [QLearningAgent Core Logic] as Core
  [Q-Tables\n(int, float, bool, byte, string)] as QTables
  [Boltzmann Module\n(Softmax Computation)] as Boltzmann
  [Temperature Control\n(Decay Over Episodes)] as Temperature
  [Action Selector] as ActionSelector
  [Environment Interaction\n(API Fuzzing)] as EnvInteraction
  [Metrics Logger] as Metrics
}

Core --> QTables : Maintain separate Q-values
Core --> Boltzmann : Send Q-values for softmax
Boltzmann --> ActionSelector : Provide action probabilities
ActionSelector --> EnvInteraction : Send selected mutations

EnvInteraction --> Core : Receive new_state, reward, done

Core --> QTables : Update Q-values (Q-Learning Update)
Core --> Temperature : Request temperature decay

Temperature --> Boltzmann : Update temperature parameter
Temperature --> Core : Updated temperature feedback

Core --> Metrics : Log cumulative rewards,\nstate visits, action counts
Metrics --> [Exploration vs Exploitation Chart]

@enduml
